                    Берлин, Вашингтон, Лондон, Мадрид, Мехико, Милан, Москва, Мюнхен,
                    Нью-Йорк, Париж, Сеул, Токио и Пекин
               </span>
            </p>
        }
        else {
            <p>
                <span class=name>Happy Route</span><span class=remark>plus flashmob</span><span class=desc>
                    Creation of schemes and determination of optimal routes.
                    Subway maps in cities are included in the samples for use and editing
                    Berlin, Washington, London, Madrid, Mexico City, Milan, Moscow, Munich,
                    New York, Paris, Seoul, Tokyo and Beijing
               </span>
            </p>
        }
    </div>

    @if (settings.Language) {
        <p class=note>* Удалены проекты, потерявшие актуальность</p>
    }
    else {
        <p class=note>* Removed projects that have lost their relevance</p>
    }
